      <title>独家：瑞安航空的奥利里在都柏林举行会议，加大对波音的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/ryanairs-oleary-will-meet-senior-boeing-execs-later-wednesday-2024-03-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞安航空首席执行官迈克尔·奥利里周三表示，随着这家美国飞机制造商的危机加深，他将于当天晚些时候在都柏林会见波音公司高管，讨论飞机交付的长期延误问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/ryanairs-oleary-will-meet-senior-boeing-execs-later-wednesday-2024-03-20/</guid>
