      <title>Kyowa Kirin 的基因疗法是美国最昂贵的药物，标价 430 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/kyowa-kirins-gene-therapy-most-expensive-us-drug-with-43-mln-price-tag-2024-03-20/</link>
